'''[[dining]] [[room]]''' (''plural'' '''dining rooms''')

#A room, in a [[home]] or [[hotel]], where [[meal]]s are [[eaten]]. Some [[restaurants]] provide private dining rooms for hire, away from the main public eating areas.

